<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Liam Hemsworth and Miley Cyrus shocked the world when they divorced in 2019 just six months after tying the knot.  </p>

<p>However, the 30-year-old actor has since moved on with model Gabriella Brooks.  </p>

<p>And, when it comes to Liam's past with his famous ex, the 24-year-old beauty 'isn't worried' by it, according to a new report. </p>

<p>Secure: A report this week claimed Liam Hemsworth's girlfriend Gabriella Brooks (pictured) 'isn't worried' about Liam's past with his ex-wife Miley Cyrus </p>

<p>'They're both secure in their relationship and Gabriella isn't worried that Liam has any lingering feelings for Miley and isn't intimidated by their relationship, an alleged source told Us Weekly.</p>

<p>'Liam and Gabriella are really close and feel comfortable with one another. They connect over important topics and share the same values about family and life.'</p>

<p>Liam and Gabriella have been dating for about nine months.   </p>

<p>Split: Liam and Miley Cyrus (pictured) shocked the world when they divorced in 2019 just six months after tying the knot</p>

<p>They were spotted together for the first time in mid-December last year as they enjoyed a lunch date in Byron Bay with Liam's parents, Craig and Leonie Hemsworth. </p>

<p>Liam married American pop-star, Miley in December 2018, but the pair split in June last year.</p>

<p>The former couple they did not publicly confirm their breakup until two months later.</p>

<p>Romance: Liam and Gabriella have been dating for about nine months. They were spotted together for the first time in mid-December last year</p>

<p>On Wednesday, Miley opened up about her marriage breakdown on the Joe Rogan Experience podcast.</p>

<p>'I recently just went through a very public divorce that f***ing sucked,' she told host Joe Rogan.</p>

<p>'What really sucked about it wasn't the fact that me and someone that I loved realised that we don't love each other the way that we used to anymore. That's okay. I can accept that.' </p>

<p>Opening up: Miley opened up about her divorce from Liam on the the Joe Rogan Experience podcast on Wednesday </p>
